g src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以用個腦諗野"},{"pid":"cddac0c762765e844817026f92991e2e74888b59","tid":1487842,"uid":245371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4VSwnBQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4VSwnBQ.jpg&h=7491b44d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請宣傳 ［824觀塘大遊行］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486089</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7c65900f53a2be31a649fbd9b329f134eb416fb4","tid":1487842,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cddac0c762765e844817026f92991e2e74888b59","tid":1487842,"uid":245371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4VSwnBQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4VSwnBQ.jpg&h=7491b44d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請宣傳 ［824觀塘大遊行］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486089</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff47aa3efc86132986da5fe269cc3a977f8d6db","tid":1487842,"uid":120123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:10:29.000Z","msg":"你都on撚尻。<br />\n我未見過有人來求診會大叫，我愛警察，我愛中共。<br />\n我屌你老母，你班警狗分唔開專業工作，同政府取態，你就唔好以為醫護人員全部好似你班毅進仔咁撚低能啦。<br />\n<br />\n我話既，我著得制服，我服務病人係根據返專業判斷，我昆你我落地獄。<br />\n但係我除左制服一定屌撚曬你班黑警老母。有咩問題???<br />\n<br />\n我仆你個街，你班死黑警，屌尻你唔係因為你係藍絲。係因為你班撚樣冇人性。"},{"pid":"0834c3e6c053282eee6cd2515764f8fef4f664c3","tid":1487842,"uid":271539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:13:31.000Z","msg":"醫務人員唔係國泰<br />\n國泰你可以經濟制裁佢<br />\n醫務人員 你有病唔好去睇醫生<br />\n如果唔係 你肯定仲慘過飲凍撚水"},{"pid":"e995eeaa78aab314469ac60a72bb9a7448f3a9cc","tid":1487842,"uid":181549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:13:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 快撚啲炒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戴黑口罩 掛住大大條係心口未撚驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申公立護士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n822 中學生集會<br />\n823 人鍊<br />\n824 觀塘 + 機場交通壓測<br />\n825 葵荃青<br />\n831 民陣<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n-撤回逃犯條例<br />\n-撤銷暴動定性<br />\n-釋放被捕義士<br />\n-成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n-實行雙真普選"},{"pid":"ade346fd465cbf9f682e6e8e5e4190615a7fa265","tid":1487842,"uid":268090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:13:54.000Z","msg":"驚未唔好睇醫生囉"},{"pid":"5a9e6a32f2dd26c4b62eedda4e5c913ba7ad491e","tid":1487842,"uid":2248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:16:00.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"9c5777795cdbb3160704adb889428ce9ffc81ea6","tid":1487842,"uid":120123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:16:14.000Z","msg":"我本身工作都唔會戴黑口罩。黑絲帶。但係我唔做，唔等於其他人唔可以做。<br />\n除非你証明到黑口罩，黑絲帶嚮infection control 角度上係有問題。<br />\n至於醫院連儂牆。好老實講，我唔讚成放嚮醫院&quot;入面&quot;，但係你放嚮醫院大堂，門口呢d地方我覺得冇問題。<br />\n點解我唔讚成放嚮醫院入面，純粹係唔想d病人，甚至serco, ISS因為政見唔同嚮度嘈生曬。"},{"pid":"2953d9593dd0e5ab8aaadc19abd992855e98bd15","tid":1487842,"uid":169665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:16:47.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意返大灣區醫啦"},{"pid":"168ae371a54d861886c25d9c4c334360076301e8","tid":1487842,"uid":120123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"